Figure 2:Improving VLM Post-training with Visual Perception Data Synthesis and Staged Training:
(a) Generating image-content based QA pairs by feeding captions to an LLM and labeling answers with a strong VLM;
(b) Perception difficulty filtering, which removes samples that can be answered by the base VLMs based on caption;
(c) Staged training by different capabilitiesfrom seeing to thinking.
